21 August 2008Government will hold Cluster media briefings on the implementation of the Government Programme of Action.The briefings will take place at the Union Buildings, Room 153 and Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town. There will be a video link-up at all briefings.Briefings schedule:Monday, 25 August 2008 9:00 - 10:30 Justice, Crime Prevention and Security Cluster Chair: Minister Charles Nqakula 13:00 - 14:30 Social Cluster Chair: Minister Manto Tshabalala MsimangNB: Governance and Administration and International Relations, Peace and Security are still being scheduled.Enquiries Harold Maloka (Pretoria) Cell: 082 847 9799Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)